---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const pageTitle       = "Download The Science of Getting Rich — Free PDF (Wallace D. Wattles)";
const pageDescription = "Published in 1910, this is the book that inspired The Secret. Wattles argues that getting rich is an exact science — not a matter of luck, talent, or envir";
const pageKeywords    = "the science of getting rich pdf, wallace d. wattles free download, the science of getting rich free, wallace d. wattles pdf";
---

<Layout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  keywords={pageKeywords}
  type="website"
  canonicalUrl="https://successodysseyhub.com/free/science-of-getting-rich"
>

<main class="free-page">

  <section class="hero" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1f15 0%, #064e3b 50%, #0a1f15 100%);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-inner">

        <div class="book-mockup">
          <div class="book-cover-art">
            <div class="book-spine" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #10b981aa, #10b981);"></div>
            <div class="book-front" style="border-color: #10b98155;">
              <p class="book-label">Wallace D. Wattles</p>
              <h2 style="color:#10b981;">The Science of Getting Rich</h2>
              <p class="book-year">Original 1910 Edition</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="book-glow" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, #10b98133 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-content">
          <span class="badge" style="background:#10b98122;color:#10b981;border-color:#10b98144;">FREE DOWNLOAD · Public Domain Classic</span>
          <h1>The book Rhonda Byrne called the inspiration for The Secret.</h1>
          <p class="hero-sub">Published in 1910, this is the book that inspired The Secret. Wattles argues that getting rich is an exact science — not a matter of luck, talent, or environment. If you do certain things in a certain way, you will get rich. Period.</p>
          <ul class="hook-list">
            <li>💰 Getting rich is not about luck — it follows precise, learnable laws</li>
            <li>🧠 The 'Certain Way' of acting that guarantees financial results</li>
            <li>🔥 Why competition actually keeps you poor — and what to do instead</li>
            <li>⚡ The book Rhonda Byrne read before writing The Secret</li>
          </ul>

          <form
            name="science-of-getting-rich-leads"
            method="POST"
            action="/free/thank-you-science-of-getting-rich"
            data-netlify="true"
            netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
            class="download-form"
          >
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="science-of-getting-rich-leads" />
            <input type="hidden" name="book" value="The Science of Getting Rich" />
            <p class="hidden"><label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>
            <div class="form-row">
              <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email address" required autocomplete="email" style="border-color:#10b98166;" />
              <button type="submit" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#10b981,#10b981cc);color:#fff;">Download Free PDF →</button>
            </div>
            <p class="form-note">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
          </form>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quotes-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Key Wisdom From the Book</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">These are not motivational quotes — these are the ideas that have shaped how millions of people think about success, purpose, and living well.</p>
      <div class="quotes-grid">
        <div class="quote-card">
          <span class="quote-num">01</span>
          <h3>The Science</h3>
          <p>"There is a science of getting rich, and it is an exact science, like algebra or arithmetic. There are certain laws which govern the process of acquiring riches."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quote-card">
          <span class="quote-num">02</span>
          <h3>Competition</h3>
          <p>"You do not have to drive sharp bargains. You do not have to act dishonestly. You do not need to take from anybody."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quote-card">
          <span class="quote-num">03</span>
          <h3>Creation</h3>
          <p>"You must get rid of the thought of competition. You are to create, not to compete for what is already created."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quote-card">
          <span class="quote-num">04</span>
          <h3>Action</h3>
          <p>"Do not wait for a change of environment before you act. Cause a change of environment through action."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quote-card">
          <span class="quote-num">05</span>
          <h3>Gratitude</h3>
          <p>"The grateful mind is constantly fixed upon the best; therefore it tends to become the best."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quote-card">
          <span class="quote-num">06</span>
          <h3>Certainty</h3>
          <p>"Hold the vision of yourself in the right business, with the purpose to get into it. Act upon your present business with the faith and purpose of the person who shall very soon enter the right business."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-box" style="border-color:#10b98144;">
        <h2>Get Your Free Copy Now</h2>
        <p>Published 1910. Still one of the most powerful books you can read.<br/>Download the original edition — completely free.</p>
        <form
          name="science-of-getting-rich-leads"
          method="POST"
          action="/free/thank-you-science-of-getting-rich"
          data-netlify="true"
          class="download-form download-form--dark"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="science-of-getting-rich-leads" />
          <input type="hidden" name="book" value="The Science of Getting Rich" />
          <input type="hidden" name="bot-field" />
          <div class="form-row">
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email address" required autocomplete="email" style="border-color:#10b98166;" />
            <button type="submit" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#10b981,#10b981cc);color:#fff;">Get Free PDF →</button>
          </div>
        </form>
        <p class="affiliate-note">
          Want a beautiful printed edition?
          <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1604591870/?tag=successodysse-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Get the hardcover on Amazon →</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Layout>

<style>
.free-page { background: var(--color-bg-primary); }
.hero { padding: 5rem 0 4rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.hero::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:-100px; right:-100px; width:400px; height:400px; background:radial-gradient(circle,#10b98122 0%,transparent 70%); border-radius:50%; }
.hero-inner { display:grid; grid-template-columns:280px 1fr; gap:4rem; align-items:center; position:relative; z-index:1; }
.book-mockup { position:relative; display:flex; justify-content:center; }
.book-glow { position:absolute; inset:-20px; filter:blur(20px); border-radius:50%; }
.book-cover-art { display:flex; position:relative; z-index:1; filter:drop-shadow(0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)); }
.book-spine { width:28px; border-radius:4px 0 0 4px; flex-shrink:0; }
.book-front { width:180px; background:linear-gradient(160deg,#0a1f15,#064e3b); border-radius:0 6px 6px 0; padding:2rem 1.5rem; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:space-between; min-height:260px; border:1px solid; border-left:none; h2{font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:900;line-height:1.1;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;margin:0;} .book-label{font-size:0.7rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;margin:0;} .book-year{font-size:0.65rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin:0;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;} }
.badge { display:inline-block; padding:0.4rem 1rem; border:1px solid; border-radius:2rem; font-size:0.78rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:1.25rem; }
.hero-content h1 { font-size:2rem; color:#fff; line-height:1.25; margin-bottom:1rem; }
.hero-sub { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size:1rem; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:1.5rem; }
.hook-list { list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0 0 2rem; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.6rem; li{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);font-size:0.95rem;} }
.download-form .form-row { display:flex; gap:0.75rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem; input[type="email"]{flex:1;padding:0.9rem 1.2rem;border:2px solid;border-radius:0.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#fff;font-size:1rem;outline:none;&::placeholder{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);}&:focus{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);};} button{padding:0.9rem 1.75rem;border:none;border-radius:0.5rem;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s;&:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);}} }
.form-note { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); font-size:0.78rem; margin:0; }
.hidden { display:none; }
.quotes-section { padding:5rem 0; background:var(--color-bg-secondary); h2{text-align:center;font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;} .section-sub{text-align:center;color:var(--color-text-secondary);max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 3rem;line-height:1.6;} }
.quotes-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(300px,1fr)); gap:1.5rem; }
.quote-card { background:var(--color-bg-primary); border:1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); padding:1.75rem; transition:var(--transition); &:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);border-color:#10b981;} .quote-num{display:block;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;color:#10b981;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:0.5rem;} h3{font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;} p{color:var(--color-text-secondary);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.6;font-style:italic;margin:0;} }
.cta-section { padding:5rem 0; }
.cta-box { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1f15,#064e3b); border:1px solid; border-radius:var(--radius-lg); padding:3.5rem; text-align:center; h2{color:#fff;font-size:1.9rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;} p{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin-bottom:2rem;line-height:1.7;} }
.download-form--dark { max-width:500px; margin:0 auto 1.5rem; input[type="email"]{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)!important;} }
.affiliate-note { font-size:0.85rem!important; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)!important; margin:0!important; a{color:#10b981;text-decoration:none;&:hover{text-decoration:underline;}} }
@media(max-width:768px) {
  .hero-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:2rem;text-align:center;}
  .book-mockup{justify-content:center;}
  .hook-list{text-align:left;}
  .download-form .form-row{flex-direction:column;button{width:100%;}}
  .hero-content h1{font-size:1.6rem;}
  .cta-box{padding:2rem 1.5rem;}
}
</style>
